Overview
Create a definition for what an agent is that can be used as an anchor for the group.  There will be a spectrum that will allow us to help identify where a specific agent lives on the range of agentic experiences.


Working Ideas
Devon Hillard
Any Service which uses AI (LLM, expert system, ML) to complete it's function.
